version_description:
All new store experience - try flipping through the stack of covers!

Completely reimagined and rebuilt for iOS 8.

New features include:
• free previews
• faster downloading
• all new interface for iOS 8
• new "stack" view
• all new grid view

Check the Stream to see what other people are sharing!

Stream update:
• faster sharing
• new upload design
• captions are now optional

Completely re-designed!
All-new catalog design.
Improved audio & video.
Login service for additional viewing options.

Search feature added
App stability improved
Compatibility with iOS 9.3.1
